<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
  <!-- Because the movie varible reprasent the array of movie objects we use for loop to loop through the array os movies and get eachmovie poster and out put it.we have a class hear as we call image responsive this is a bootstrap class -->
